SUMMARY:Kickstands Up! Gallery Talk with Pacific Northwest Museum of Motorc
	ycling
DTSTAMP:20260315T165636Z
DTSTART:20260328T140000Z
DESCRIPTION:Dive deeper into Kickstands Up: 125 Years of Motorcycling in th
	e Pacific Northwest with gallery talks by exhibit co-curators from the Pac
	ific Northwest Museum of Motorcycling. Roll on down to MOHAI and learn mor
	e about the bikes and riders that have made history. \\nSpots are limited 
	and are assigned on a first-come\\\, first-served basis. \\nFor accessibil
	ity support\\\, please contact programs@mohai.org two weeks before the eve
	nt.\n\nhttps://mohai.org/event/kickstands-up-gallery-talk-with-pacific-nor
	thwest-museum-of-motorcycling/\n\nFrom MOHAI - Museum of History & Industr
	y
